<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Canceled by Doctor - SID Clinic</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #334155;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grid" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" stroke-width="0.5"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grid)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 180px;
            height: 90px;
            border-radius: 5%;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 45px 35px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 25px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);
        }
        
        .status-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }
        
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #475569;
        }
        
        .doctor-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .doctor-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
        }
        
        .doctor-card h3 {
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .doctor-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .doctor-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }
        
        .cancellation-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.08);
        }
        
        .cancellation-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
        }
        
        .cancellation-card h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .cancel-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #dc2626;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        
        .icon-circle {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        
        .cancel-reason {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .cancel-reason h4 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .warning-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .appointment-id-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .appointment-id-section strong {
            color: #235f8b;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.05);
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #235f8b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .steps-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .steps-list li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #235f8b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #235f8b 0%, #1a4f7a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(35, 95, 139, 0.4);
        }
        
        .button-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 35px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer h3 {
            color: #60a5fa;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #60a5fa;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #374151;
        }
        
        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .contact-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #60a5fa;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .disclaimer {
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #374151;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            
            .container {
                border-radius: 12px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 8px;
                padding: 12px 0;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .contact-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="https://sidclinic.com/logo.jpeg" alt="SID Clinic Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1>Appointment Canceled by Doctor</h1>
                <p>We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience this may cause</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">
                <div class="status-icon">‚úï</div>
                Appointment Canceled
            </div>
            
            <div class="greeting">Dear {{recipientName}},</div>
            
            <p class="intro-text">
                We regret to inform you that your upcoming appointment has been canceled by your healthcare provider. 
                We understand this may cause inconvenience to your schedule, and we sincerely apologize for any disruption this may cause.
            </p>
            
            <div class="doctor-card">
                <h3>
                    <div class="doctor-icon">Dr</div>
                    Canceling Physician
                </h3>
                <div class="doctor-name">Dr. {{cancelerName}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cancellation-card">
                <h3>
                    <div class="cancel-icon">‚úï</div>
                    Canceled Appointment Details
                </h3>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <div class="icon-circle">üìÖ</div>
                        Date
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <div class="icon-circle">üïê</div>
                        Time
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">
                        <div class="icon-circle">#</div>
                        Appointment ID
                    </span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentId}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if cancelReason}}
            <div class="cancel-reason">
                <h4>
                    <div class="warning-icon">!</div>
                    Reason for Cancellation
                </h4>
                <p style="color: #92400e; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">{{cancelReason}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>
                    <div class="steps-icon">‚Üí</div>
                    What You Can Do Next
                </h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        Schedule a new appointment with Dr. {{cancelerName}} at an alternative time
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        Browse our available physicians and book with another specialist
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        Contact our patient support team for personalized assistance
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        Check our real-time availability calendar for immediate openings
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="appointment-id-section">
                <strong>Reference ID for Future Communications: {{appointmentId}}</strong>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">
                    <div class="button-icon">+</div>
                    Schedule New Appointment
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
                Our patient care team is standing by to assist you with rescheduling or addressing any concerns you may have.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <h3>
                <div class="footer-icon">üè•</div>
                SID Clinic
            </h3>
            <p>Dedicated to providing exceptional healthcare services with integrity, professionalism, and patient-centered care.</p>
            
            <div class="contact-grid">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">@</div>
                    <span>Office@sidclinic.com</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">üìû</div>
                    <span>9274557987</span>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">üåê</div>
                    <span>www.sidclinic.com</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="disclaimer">
                This is an automated notification. Please do not reply directly to this email.
                For assistance, please contact us through our official channels listed above.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>